WEBVTT

00:07:30.541 --> 00:07:33.224
the most punishing forms of student debt.

00:07:34.002 --> 00:07:35.153
And it is they,

00:07:35.177 --> 00:07:36.558
curiously and sadly,

00:07:36.582 --> 00:07:40.391
who are marketed most loudly
about this college premium thing.

00:07:41.986 --> 00:07:44.383
That's not just cynical marketing,

00:07:44.407 --> 00:07:45.557
that's cruel.

00:07:47.277 --> 00:07:48.427
So what do we do?

00:07:49.279 --> 00:07:54.888
What if students and parents treated
higher education as a consumer product?

00:07:56.199 --> 00:07:57.738
Everybody else seems to.

00:07:58.686 --> 00:08:00.948
Then, like any other consumer product,